member.example:
An example dictionary:
{ MTC => URN:OASIS:NAMES:TC:XLIFF:MATCHES:2.0 }
{ MDA => URN:OASIS:NAMES:TC:XLIFF:METADATA:2.0 }.

member.param:
If true, the prefixes of the selector path will be validated as if they are
            for extensions or modules. If false, the prefixes won't be validated meaning they may be from core elements,
            extensions, or modules.
